imitation_3L1.name: Meryl
imitation_3L1.description: Born in Warren Snowfield, I had been dreaming of getting away and traveling the world. But when I was 14, an avalanche destroyed our shelter. Both my parents died and only I survived, as they had covered me with their bodies. I was rescued by the church that came to preach. After 4 years of living with them, I was selected as the Executor of the church, responsible for eliminating the heretics among us.
